Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哟  来得挺早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,依旧是家生意惨淡的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦  夜晚可热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,之前那张照片是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这玩意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,NERvGear后继机型——AmuSphere用的MMO游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这和SAO一样是VRMMO游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alf  heim  Online？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,发音应该是爱尔芙海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(367,335)\fsp4}ALfheim
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是妖精的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的国度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是款很温和的游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不  似乎不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,完全技能制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,重视玩家技巧  而且推荐PK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,完全技能制？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是不存在等级的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,各种技能反复使用后只会有一定提升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而战斗靠的则是玩家的运动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,难度还真高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就相当于没有剑技却有魔法的SAO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,据说这款游戏现在大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,原因好像是因为能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精自然拥有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听说游戏搭载了什么飞行引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯后就能自由飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那要怎么控制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不过好像相当困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然  毕竟要操控人类本没有的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是不是运动背部肌肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,热卖的游戏和亚丝娜究竟有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很像…亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然也是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,照片上的是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是游戏里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在ALfheim  Online里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那里好像叫世界树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在这棵树的上方有座传说中的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,玩家分为九大种族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为最先抵达城堡而展开竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,飞上去不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听说有什么滞空时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因此不能无限飞行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,五名玩家按体型大小叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,像多级火箭般接力飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,行为很蠢  但想法不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管他们连世界树最底的树枝也到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但却拍到了好几张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一张拍到了非常怪异的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,鸟笼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,将那个鸟笼放大到最大分辨率后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就得到这张照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但亚丝娜为什么会在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,RCT  progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明日奈的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠我才得以维持
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾基尔  这个游戏软件能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  你是要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去亲眼确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以复活的游戏算得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先去买主机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用NERvGear就可以运行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,AmuSphere不过是NERvGear的安全加强版
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要救出亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我们的战斗永远看不到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  改天在这里来一次线下聚会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是个笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还…还以为会噎死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,吃东西别那么急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小直  关于昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏小直我才能重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会把亚丝娜带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  我也想见见亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定能成为好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一周后的1月26日  婚礼将在这间病房里举行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会叫你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次借我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,开始连接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到ALfheim  Online
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,首先请输入性别和角色名称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊  你就是那位英雄桐人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(407,335)\fsp0}Kirito
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来请决定种族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请从九大种族中选择一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就选它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,确定选择守卫精灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(347,335)\fsp1}Spriggan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,角色样貌将随机生成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是否继续
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.00,SPEC4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)\fs19}守卫精灵{\r}\N \N领地位于爱尔芙海姆东北方，\N以古代遗迹为首都。\N敏捷度高以及擅长幻属性魔法。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,即将传送至守卫精灵的出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,祝您好运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:46.77,SPEC,,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(500,0)}爱尔芙海姆·中立地带·古森林\N2025年1月20日
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,前不久才发生过那种倒霉事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.68,SPEC3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}野外地图上无法即时退出。是否退出？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,角色状态是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,出BUG了？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,技能
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,单手剑
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,飞剑
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,武器防御
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,战时回复
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,探敌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,追踪
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,隐藏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,夜视
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,增加重量上限
Comment: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,疾走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和SAO内的数值一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道是SAO内部？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托一定要有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你还认得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又见面了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去吃东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,奇迹是会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这里其实不是SAO里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这里叫ALfheim  Online  是另一个游戏世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有可能是「刀剑神域」服务器的备份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(321,335)\fsp-1}Sword Art Online
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,备份？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,基础程序群和图形形式都完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是Cardinal系统的版本稍微有点旧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原本运营SAO的ARGUS的处理结果是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,将运营交由RECT承担
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是RECT吸收了ARGUS的技术资产
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并进行了挪用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么会有我的个人资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看爸爸的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这和爸爸在SAO里使用的角色资料相一致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可能因为存档格式几乎一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以覆盖了两个游戏共通技能的熟练度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来  双刀流的确没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,至于道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看来已经损坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是在惹来检错程序之前删除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.54,SPEC3.5,,0,0,0,,是否删除全部道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.71,SPEC3.5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}是否删除全部道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那技能熟练度怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,至于技能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要人类的游戏管理员不直接查看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就不会有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来  我连封弊者都不算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而变成一个纯粹的作弊者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,结衣你现在又是怎样一个状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,用作辅助玩家的模拟人格程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,属于导航精灵一类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是变化成精灵时的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还和以前一样拥有管理员权限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不  顶多只能进行查阅以及登录广域地图数据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其实呢  亚丝娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈她好像在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亚丝娜在攻略SAO之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,依然没有回归现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到有情报说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在爱尔芙海姆目击到像亚丝娜的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道了大概的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个叫世界树的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈就在那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来  我怎么会来到这片荒凉的森林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,按理应该传送到出生地才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是位置信息损坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,又或者是信号受到了干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,既然那样  把我送到世界树附近不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才能飞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像能用辅助摇杆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,举起左手  做出握拳的手势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,往跟前拉是上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,推下去是下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而左右则是转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,按住按钮是加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而松开则是减速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,翅膀发光时可以飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,经过一定时间后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,必须让翅膀休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊  基本明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  离这里最近的城镇是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,西面有属于风精灵的城镇——司伊鲁班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(282,335)\fsp1}Sylph
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那里就是最…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有玩家在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,莉…莉法  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,加把劲  雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要成功逃到风精灵的领地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雷根  回避！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,万不得已  做好战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,打不赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,西格鲁特他们肯定已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽量多吸引一些敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而你要自己想办法打倒一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也要让我看看你英勇的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这下能赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  别停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要怨我  我只是执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放下钱和道具  我就网开一面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你装什么绅士啊  影宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没遇上女人当对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆把她杀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算死也要再带一个人上路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谁不怕死亡惩罚就放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脾气真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别怪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,会飞还要懂着陆才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,三个重战士欺负一个女孩子  也太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,区区一个菜鸟还够胆跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就如你所愿  让你死在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以用剑砍他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然…没什么不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少对方是有那样的敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  被囚的女王
